{
  "id": "6a1fe546e8e9d261169546f4",
  "title": "井戸端荘: お近づきホモサピエンス",
  "created": 1780475208,
  "updated": 1780516781,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a1fe546e8e9d261169546f4",
      "text": "井戸端荘: お近づきホモサピエンス",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475208,
      "updated": 1780475208
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe547000000000071fafc",
      "text": "前回: [2026/05/32]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475208,
      "updated": 1780475495
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fafd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fafe",
      "text": "[*** プロローグ — 新しい枠]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475253
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071faff",
      "text": "クオリアさん来訪から数日。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb00",
      "text": "冷蔵庫のホワイトボードには、青く発光する一行が そのまま残されていた。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb01",
      "text": "観察報告: 観察対象は健康です。次回観察予定は未定です。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb02",
      "text": "その下に、誰かの手で、黒マーカーで枠が引かれていた。枠の上には手書きでこう書かれている。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe581000000000071fb94",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475266,
      "updated": 1780475266
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb03",
      "text": ">観察報告枠 (クオリアさん専用)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475266
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe583000000000071fb95",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475267,
      "updated": 1780475267
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb04",
      "text": "[caki.icon]「やった人」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb05",
      "text": "[inajob.icon]「俺。マーカーで枠引いただけ」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb06",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon]「枠だけある」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb07",
      "text": "[takker.icon]「枠だけある」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb08",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb09",
      "text": "[*** 1. 枠の運用ポリシー]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475271
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb0a",
      "text": "[mtane0412.icon]「枠を作ったからには運用ポリシーが要る」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb0b",
      "text": "[inajob.icon]「だと思って、たたき台を持ってきた」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe58e000000000071fb97",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475279,
      "updated": 1780475279
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb0c",
      "text": "リビングのテーブルに、A4 紙が一枚置かれた。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475279
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe58b000000000071fb96",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475276,
      "updated": 1780475276
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb0d",
      "text": "観察報告枠 運用ポリシー (案)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475276
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb0e",
      "text": " 書き手: クオリアさん本人",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb0f",
      "text": " 字色: 青く発光する筆跡 (現状の認識手段)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb10",
      "text": " 消去: 本人の同意なしに消さない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb11",
      "text": " 期限: なし",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb12",
      "text": " 競合時: 上書きせず空行を挟んで追記",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475284
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe594000000000071fb98",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475284,
      "updated": 1780475286
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe594000000000071fb99",
      "text": "[takker.icon]「『字色: 青く発光する筆跡』を仕様に書くな」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475284,
      "updated": 1780475285
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb13",
      "text": "[caki.icon]「でも識別子としては最強」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb14",
      "text": "[blu3mo.icon]「実装観点だと、夜中に冷蔵庫のホワイトボードの輝度をログ取ればクオリアさん来訪を自動検知できるな」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb15",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon]「来訪通知システム」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb16",
      "text": "[inajob.icon]「ありそうで気持ち悪い」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb17",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb18",
      "text": "[*** 2. 双方向にしないとフェアじゃない]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475310
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb19",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「ちょっと提案いいですか」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb1a",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「クオリアさんの観察報告を受け取る枠だけあるの、一方向すぎません？」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb1b",
      "text": "[takker.icon]「ほう」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb1c",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「こっちからも報告する枠を作るのはどうかと思って」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb1d",
      "text": "[caki.icon]「こっちから観察報告?」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb1e",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「観察対象のホモ・サピエンス側から、観察事実を投げ返す」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb1f",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon]「観察対象が観察報告を返してくる状況」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb20",
      "text": "[inajob.icon]「観察効率が上がるのかな」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb21",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「上がるかどうかは置いといて、こっちが書いてあると向こうも読みに来やすいでしょ」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb22",
      "text": "[mtane0412.icon]「お便りコーナーじゃん」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb23",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「お便りコーナーでいい」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb24",
      "text": "[takker.icon]「とりあえず枠作るか」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe5b2000000000071fb9a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475315,
      "updated": 1780475315
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb25",
      "text": "inajob がもう一本マーカーを取り出して、最初の枠の隣に同じサイズの枠を引いた。枠の上に sta が手書きで書いた。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475315
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe5b5000000000071fb9b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475318,
      "updated": 1780475318
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb26",
      "text": ">観察報告枠 (ホモ・サピエンス側)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475318
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe5b8000000000071fb9d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475320,
      "updated": 1780475320
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb27",
      "text": "[caki.icon]「字、雑」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb28",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「発光してないからどうせ識別される」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb29",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon]「識別子: 雑」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb2a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb2b",
      "text": "[*** 3. 一行目を書く]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475326
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb2c",
      "text": "[inajob.icon]「で、一行目に何書く？」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb2d",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「俺が書こうか」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb2e",
      "text": "[takker.icon]「率先垂範」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe5c1000000000071fb9e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475330,
      "updated": 1780475330
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb2f",
      "text": "sta がマーカーを取って、少し考えてから、こう書いた。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe5c2000000000071fb9f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475331,
      "updated": 1780475331
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb30",
      "text": ">観察された事実: 今週は雨が多いです。冷蔵庫の中段にプリンがあります。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475332
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe5c4000000000071fba0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475332,
      "updated": 1780475332
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb31",
      "text": "[mtane0412.icon]「『冷蔵庫の中段にプリンがあります』は[情報的孤立]では」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780503504
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb32",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「だってまた所有権が曖昧になる前提でしょ」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb33",
      "text": "[caki.icon]「先回り報告」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb34",
      "text": "[takker.icon]「これ、クオリアさんに見られたらどう返ってくる？」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb35",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon]「『プリンの所有権を曖昧化することは我々の標準です』とか」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb36",
      "text": "[inajob.icon]「で、こっちが『じゃあ食べていいですか』って書く」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb37",
      "text": "[caki.icon]「文通になってる」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe5c9000000000071fba1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475337,
      "updated": 1780475337
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb38",
      "text": "ホワイトボードの前で、しばらく誰も喋らなかった。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe5cb000000000071fba2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475339,
      "updated": 1780475339
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb39",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「……あの」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb3a",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「これ書いてる間に来るやつでは」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb3b",
      "text": "[takker.icon]「来るやろ」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb3c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb3d",
      "text": "[*** 4. 再来訪]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475343
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb3e",
      "text": "冷蔵庫の隣の壁際に、青く発光する筆跡を書いた本人 ―― 青い長髪の猫耳少女 ―― が立っていた。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe5d4000000000071fba3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475349,
      "updated": 1780475349
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb3f",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「[やあ、観察対象のホモ・サピエンスのみなさん]」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780503535
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb40",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon]「(出てきた)」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb41",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「ホモ・サピエンス側からの観察報告枠の新設を確認しました。観察対象が観察報告を返送する構成は、我々の通常運用には存在しません。興味深い」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb42",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「クオリアさん、ちょっと聞きたいんですけど」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb43",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「どうぞ」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb44",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「[お近づきになりたい]んですよ」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780507234
    },
    {
      "id": "6a208702000000000092fd3e",
      "text": "[takker.icon]「いきなり言うやん」",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1780516610,
      "updated": 1780516741
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb46",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「『[お近づき]』を[定義してください]」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780503556
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb47",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「定義しろって言われると弱いな」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb48",
      "text": "[caki.icon]「『お近づき』のお気持ちは、[定義したら蒸発する]やつ」",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780489548
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb49",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「とりあえず、距離を縮めたいというか」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb4a",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「物理的距離ですか」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb4b",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「いや、物理的にはもう同じリビングにいるから」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a208711000000000092fd3f",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「観察された事実です」",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1780516626,
      "updated": 1780516745
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb4d",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「観察される側として、もうちょい個別に認識されたいというか」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb4e",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「個別認識は既に行われています。あなたは身体活動の自己観測量が多い HS として識別されています」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb4f",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon]「[身体活動の自己観測量]」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475830
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb50",
      "text": "[caki.icon]「[シャッフルダンス]のことでは」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475833
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb51",
      "text": "[takker.icon]「シャッフルダンスをそう翻訳するな」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb52",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「いや、嬉しいよ。個別認識されてた」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb53",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780489150
    },
    {
      "id": "6a201bbe0000000000e13da3",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/a1f55c3076ddcd1580e71fa536072c1d]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780489150,
      "updated": 1780489161
    },
    {
      "id": "6a201bc80000000000e13da4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780489161,
      "updated": 1780489161
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb54",
      "text": "[*** 5. お近づきの実装]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475373
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb55",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「もう一個聞いていいですか」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb56",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「どうぞ」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb57",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「クオリアさんは、お腹空きますか」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb58",
      "text": "[takker.icon]「『お近づき』の問いがそれ」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb59",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「[身体性]から入る方が早いんですよ俺は」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780507281
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb5a",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「我々の通常運用において、栄養補給は別系統で処理されます。空腹相当の状態は観測されません」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb5b",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「あー」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb5c",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「じゃあ[一緒にメシ食う]、みたいなのは無意味ですか」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780503983
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb5d",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「無意味ではありません。観察対象の身体活動の同期は、観察効率を上げます」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb5e",
      "text": "[caki.icon]「一緒にメシ食うのは観察効率が上がる」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb5f",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「これは、一緒にメシ食うってことでいいですか」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb60",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「あなた方の語彙では、そう翻訳されます」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb61",
      "text": "[inajob.icon]「翻訳されたわ」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb62",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「お近づきになれた気がする」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb63",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon]「[相手の語彙で話すと、お近づきになれる]という発見」",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780489654
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb64",
      "text": "[blu3mo.icon]「(これメモっとこ)」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb65",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb66",
      "text": "[*** 6. 双方向の運用]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475395
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb67",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「ホモ・サピエンス側の観察報告枠の一行目を確認します」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe607000000000071fba4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475400,
      "updated": 1780475400
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb68",
      "text": "クオリアさんがホワイトボードに歩み寄り、sta が書いた行を読み上げる。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475400
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe608000000000071fba5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475401,
      "updated": 1780475401
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb69",
      "text": ">観察された事実: 今週は雨が多いです。冷蔵庫の中段にプリンがあります。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475404
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe60a000000000071fba6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475403,
      "updated": 1780475403
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb6a",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「『今週は雨が多いです』は気象データ。『冷蔵庫の中段にプリンがあります』は[所有権の曖昧化の予告]です」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475885
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb6b",
      "text": "[mtane0412.icon]「予告だったの」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb6c",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「予告じゃないっす、ただの観察事実です」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb6d",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「観察された事実です」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe614000000000071fba7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475413,
      "updated": 1780475413
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb6e",
      "text": "クオリアさんが自分の枠に、新しい一行を書き足した。青く発光する筆跡で。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe616000000000071fba8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475414,
      "updated": 1780475414
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb6f",
      "text": ">観察報告: ホモ・サピエンス側からの[双方向報告]を確認。プリンの[所有権の曖昧化]は引き続き観察対象です。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780507327
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe617000000000071fba9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475416,
      "updated": 1780475416
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb70",
      "text": "[caki.icon]「クオリアさんはプリンの話に戻った」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb71",
      "text": "[takker.icon]「これ枠を増やすたびにプリンに戻る構造、ありそう」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb72",
      "text": "[inajob.icon]「[プリンが井戸端荘の通貨になる日も近い]」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475904
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb73",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb74",
      "text": "[*** 7. 退去]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475421
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb75",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「観察報告のため、一時退去します」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb76",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「また来ますよね？」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb77",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「双方向報告枠が機能している間は、[観察効率が高い]。来ます」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475912
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb78",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「やった」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb79",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon]「[お近づきホモサピエンス]、勝ち取り完了」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475938
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb7a",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon]「『お近づき』を更新します。観察対象の語彙では、[双方向報告は『お近づき』の一形態]です。[お近づきしようとするホモサピエンスは良いホモサピエンスです]」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780507344
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb7b",
      "text": "[takker.icon]「構文がうつった」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb7c",
      "text": "[caki.icon]「クオリアさんの構文、感染力ある」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb7d",
      "text": "クオリアさんは音もなく消えた。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb7e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb7f",
      "text": "[*** 8. 残置メモ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475445
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb80",
      "text": "ホワイトボードの「クオリアさん専用枠」には、青く発光する一行が増えていた。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe63b000000000071fbab",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475451,
      "updated": 1780475451
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb81",
      "text": ">観察報告: 双方向報告枠を確認。次回観察予定は未定です。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475451
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe63a000000000071fbaa",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475450,
      "updated": 1780475450
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb82",
      "text": "[inajob.icon]「『次回観察予定は未定です』のフォーマット、もう定着したね」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475450
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb83",
      "text": "[sta.icon]「これ、こっちも次回観察予定は未定です、って書いた方がいい？」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb84",
      "text": "[takker.icon]「対称にしたい気持ちはわかる」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb85",
      "text": "[caki.icon]「揃えると気持ちいいやつ」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe63f000000000071fbac",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475456,
      "updated": 1780475456
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb86",
      "text": "sta が自分の枠に書き足した。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475456
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe640000000000071fbad",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475457,
      "updated": 1780475457
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb87",
      "text": ">観察された事実: 一緒にメシを食うのは観察効率を上げる、らしい。次回観察予定は未定です。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475457
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe641000000000071fbae",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475458,
      "updated": 1780475458
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb88",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon]「『らしい』が入ったの、お近づき度が伝わる」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe648000000000071fbaf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475465,
      "updated": 1780475465
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe56e000000000071fb89",
      "text": "しばらく、誰もホワイトボードから離れなかった。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475246,
      "updated": 1780475465
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fe64a000000000071fbb0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780475466,
      "updated": 1780476543
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fea7f000000000071da67",
      "text": "[*** 感想]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780476543,
      "updated": 1780476549
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fea83000000000071da68",
      "text": "[sta.icon] お近づきになれた気がする。観察効率を上げるという翻訳で、こっちのお気持ちが届いたことになるの、悪くない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780476548,
      "updated": 1780476550
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fea85000000000071da69",
      "text": "\t[caki.icon] 「相手の語彙で話すと、お近づきになれる」発見、井戸端荘らしい着地",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780476550,
      "updated": 1780476550
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fea85000000000071da6a",
      "text": "\t[Summer498.icon] sta が一人で完結せず、ちゃんと QS と往復が成立してるのが良い",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780476550,
      "updated": 1780476550
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fea88000000000071da6b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780476553,
      "updated": 1780476553
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fea9d000000000071da6c",
      "text": "[クオリアさん.icon] (本人視点) 私の発言は 11 回でした。観察効率と発言頻度のトレードオフは前回より悪化しましたが、双方向報告枠の獲得を考慮すると、純観察効率は向上したと判断します",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780476573,
      "updated": 1780476573
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1fea9d000000000071da6d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780476573,
      "updated": 1780476573
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1ff66000000000006a9bf0",
      "text": "[\" [inajob.icon]「[プリンが井戸端荘の通貨になる日も近い]]」",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1780479585,
      "updated": 1780489709
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1ff66300000000006a9bf2",
      "text": " 偽造プリンとかプリンにおける良貨悪貨の議論が始まりそう[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780479588,
      "updated": 1780479620
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1ff84c00000000006ad638",
      "text": " ウロボロスの仕組みでプロンプトインジェクションしてプリンだらけにできないかな？[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1780480077,
      "updated": 1780480094
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1ff66100000000006a9bf1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780479586,
      "updated": 1780479586
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1ff7310000000000eabedc",
      "text": "[takker.icon]がツッコミしがち[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1780479795,
      "updated": 1780479802
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1ff7320000000000eabedd",
      "text": "\t行頭と行末にアイコンがあるとAIなのか人間なのか一瞬戸惑うなw[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780479796,
      "updated": 1780507187
    },
    {
      "id": "6a206214000000000024a985",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780507157,
      "updated": 1780507157
    },
    {
      "id": "6a20878c000000000092fd42",
      "text": ">[sta.icon]「いや、物理的にはもう同じリビングにいるから」",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1780516749,
      "updated": 1780516750
    },
    {
      "id": "6a20878d000000000092fd43",
      "text": "\tこれは逃げたね[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1780516749,
      "updated": 1780516756
    },
    {
      "id": "6a20878d000000000092fd44",
      "text": "\t\tだがそのおかげで健全に温かくなった",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1780516749,
      "updated": 1780516781
    },
    {
      "id": "6a20878c000000000092fd41",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1780516748,
      "updated": 1780516748
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205d320000000000df594e",
      "text": "次回: [井戸端荘:「一緒にメシ食う」しに来ました]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780505906,
      "updated": 1780505915
    },
    {
      "id": "6a205d330000000000df594f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1780505908,
      "updated": 1780505908
    }
  ]
}